ber 1991) was a Romanian footballer and [[Manager (association football)|manager]].<ref>{{WorldFootball|iosif-lengheriu}}</ref><ref>{{NFT|34794}}</ref><ref name=ocna>{{cite web|url=https://www.ocnamuresonline.ro/1405-nscut-in-ocna-mure-iosif-lengheriu|title=OCNAMURESENI: N\u0103scut \u00een Ocna Mure\u015f: Iosif Lengheriu|publisher=fcsteaua.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=\nOCNA MURES PEOPLE: Born in Ocna Mures: Iosif Lengheriu |date= 28 August 2012|accessdate= 26 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nIosif Lengheriu played seven games at international level for [[Romania national football team|Romania]], making his debut in a friendly which ended with a 1\u20130 loss against [[Italy national football team|Italy]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=12039|title=Iosif Lengheriu|publisher=European Football|accessdate=26 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_match.php?id=6183|title=Romania \u2013 Italy 0:1|publisher=European Football|accessdate=26 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gsp.ro/fotbal/nationala/11-fotbalisti-romani-au-debutat-la-nationala-contra-italiei-vezi-cine-sint-216057.html|title=11 fotbali\u015fti rom\u00e2ni au debutat la \u00abna\u0163ional\u0103\u00bb contra Italiei. Vezi cine s\u00eent!|publisher=Gsp.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=11 Romanian footballers made their national debut against Italy. See who they are! |date= 17 November 2010|accessdate= 26 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n===Player===\n'''Rapid Bucure\u015fti'''\n*[[Cupa Rom\u00e2niei]]: [[1936\u201337 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1936\u201337]], [[1937\u201338 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1937\u201338]], [[1938\u201339 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1938\u201339]], [[1939\u201340 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1939\u201340]], [[1940\u201341 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1940\u201341]], [[1941\u201342 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1941\u201342]]<ref name=RS/><ref name=ocna/>\n===Manager===\n'''Farul Constan\u021ba'''\n*[[Liga II|Divizia B]]: [[Divizia B 1957\u201358|1957\u201358]]\n'''Foresta F\u0103lticeni'''\n*[[Cupa Rom\u00e2niei]] runner-up: [[1966\u201367 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1966\u201367]]<ref name=ocna/>\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/profil/iosif-lengheriu-1191/ Iosif Lengheriu player profile] at Labtof.ro\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/profil/iosif-lengheriu-6693/ Iosif Lengheriu manager profile] at Labtof.ro\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Iosif Lengheriu managerial positions\n|list1=\n{{FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti managers}}\n{{FC Farul Constan\u021ba managers}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lengheriu, Iosif}}\n[[Category:1914 births]]\n[[Category:1991 deaths]]\n[[Category:Romanian footballers]]\n[[Category:Romania international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:Liga II players]]\n[[Category:FC Unirea Alba Iulia players]]\n[[Category:ACF Gloria Bistri\u021ba players]]\n[[Category:FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti players]]\n[[Category:Romanian football managers]]\n[[Category:FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti managers]]\n[[Category:FC Farul Constan\u021ba managers]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Romanian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Iosif Lengheriu\n| image       = \n| image_size  = \n| fullname    = <!-- if different -->\n| birth_date  = {{Birth date|1914|05|24|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Ocna Mure\u0219|Uioara]], [[Romania]]<ref name=RS>{{RomanianSoccer|1063/iosif-lengheriu.htm}}</ref>\n| death_date  = {{Death date and age|1999|09|11|1914|05|24|df=y}}<ref name=RS/>\n| death_place = \n| height      = \n| position    =  [[Midfielder]]<ref name=RS/>\n| years1 = 1933\u20131934 |clubs1 = [[FC Unirea Alba Iulia|Mihai Vitezul Alba Iulia]]   |caps1 =  |goals1 = \n| years2 = 1934\u20131935 |clubs2 = [[ACF Gloria Bistri\u021ba|Ceramica Bistri\u021ba]] |caps2 =  |goals2 = \n| years3 = 1935\u20131936 |clubs3 = [[Cri\u0219ana Oradea]]      |caps3 = 19 |goals3 = 9\n| years4 = 1936\u20131946 |clubs4 = [[FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|Rapid Bucure\u0219ti]]{{efn|name=\"RAP\"|The [[Divizia A 1940\u201341]] was the last season before [[World War II]] and the [[Divizia A 1946\u201347]] was the first one after, so the appearances and goals scored during this period for [[FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|Rapid Bucure\u0219ti]] are not official.<ref name=RS/>}}        |caps4 = 82 |goals4 = 14\n| years5 = 1946\u20131948 |clubs5 = Grivi\u021ba CFR Bucure\u0219ti        |caps5 =  |goals5 = \n| totalcaps = 101 | totalgoals = 23\n| nationalyears1 = 1939\u20131941     |nationalteam1 = [[Romania national football team|Romania]]|  nationalcaps1 =7 |nationalgoals1 = 0\n| manageryears1 = 1946 |managerclubs1 = [[FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|Rapid Bucure\u0219ti]]\n| manageryears2 = 1955 |managerclubs2 = [[FC CFR Timi\u0219oara|CFR Timi\u0219oara]]\n| manageryears3 = 1956\u20131960 |managerclubs3 = [[FC Farul Constan\u021ba|Farul Constan\u021ba]]\n| manageryears4 = 1965\u20131966 |managerclubs4 = [[Foresta F\u0103lticeni]]\n}}\n\n'''Iosif Lengheriu''' (24 May 1914 - 11 September 1999) was a Romanian footballer and [[Manager (association football)|manager]].<ref>{{WorldFootball|iosif-lengheriu}}</ref><ref>{{NFT|34794}}</ref><ref name=ocna>{{cite web|url=https://www.ocnamuresonline.ro/1405-nscut-in-ocna-mure-iosif-lengheriu|title=OCNAMURESENI: N\u0103scut \u00een Ocna Mure\u015f: Iosif Lengheriu|publisher=fcsteaua.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=\nOCNA MURES PEOPLE: Born in Ocna Mures: Iosif Lengheriu |date= 28 August 2012|accessdate= 26 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nIosif Lengheriu played seven games at international level for [[Romania national football team|Romania]], making his debut in a friendly which ended with a 1\u20130 loss against [[Italy national football team|Italy]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=12039|title=Iosif Lengheriu|publisher=European Football|accessdate=26 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_match.php?id=6183|title=Romania - Italy 0:1|publisher=European Football|accessdate=26 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gsp.ro/fotbal/nationala/11-fotbalisti-romani-au-debutat-la-nationala-contra-italiei-vezi-cine-sint-216057.html|title=11 fotbali\u015fti rom\u00e2ni au debutat la \u00abna\u0163ional\u0103\u00bb contra Italiei. Vezi cine s\u00eent!|publisher=Gsp.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=11 Romanian footballers made their national debut against Italy. See who they are! |date= 17 November 2010|accessdate= 26 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n===Player===\n'''Rapid Bucure\u015fti'''\n*[[Cupa Rom\u00e2niei]]: [[1936\u201337 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1936\u201337]], [[1937\u201338 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1937\u201338]], [[1938\u201339 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1938\u201339]], [[1939\u201340 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1939\u201340]], [[1940\u201341 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1940\u201341]], [[1941\u201342 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1941\u201342]]<ref name=RS/><ref name=ocna/>\n===Manager===\n'''Farul Constan\u021ba'''\n*[[Liga II|Divizia B]]: [[Divizia B 1957\u201358|1957\u201358]]\n'''Foresta F\u0103lticeni'''\n*[[Cupa Rom\u00e2niei]] runner-up: [[1966\u201367 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|1966\u201367]]<ref name=ocna/>\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/profil/iosif-lengheriu-1191/ Iosif Lengheriu player profile] at Labtof.ro\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/profil/iosif-lengheriu-6693/ Iosif Lengheriu manager profile] at Labtof.ro\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Iosif Lengheriu managerial positions\n|list1=\n{{FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti managers}}\n{{FC Farul Constan\u021ba managers}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lengheriu, Iosif}}\n[[Category:1914 births]]\n[[Category:1999 deaths]]\n[[Category:Romanian footballers]]\n[[Category:Romania international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:Liga II players]]\n[[Category:FC Unirea Alba Iulia players]]\